{"tid":1312670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察都係打份工 唔應該對佢地採取行動 應該對準政權","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T15:10:46.000Z","uid":26680,"like":97,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b453ec02787aaa630a8ec7d275d7138104ef019","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你都on撚鳩</span></span><br />\n我先唔講雨傘<br />\n由六月到依加仲做緊警察嘅 都係佢地自己揀要助紂為虐<br />\n佢地就係政府打壓人民嘅機器<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對準警察就係對準政權</span></span><br />\n唔好再咁戇鳩覺得佢地係二元分立<br />\n要有差別對待或者手下留情<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動就係反對政權嘅表達方法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非 採取行動爭取成立獨委會"},{"pid":"cd6a41838b0c2b1c52895814c6a18ca499693317","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7af552b5ba8b0ba569ebe93033c939f90e2c902","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cc5fba6c89ce768d7139aa46e8486d8daefd5e","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804cb623372679c3eff7dcfb196fe28f33d90260","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58d00180feee6d020505af4934adee3b8937549","tid":1312670,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f68b1243e7326561c5277da